Find all the git files:
  find ~/* -name ".git"

Changes to the git:
  git status
  git add
  git commit /-a                             (Skipping staging area)
  git commit -a -m 'Comment directly'        (Skipping editir changes)

Log of the activities:
  git log --pretty=format:"%h - %an, %ar : %s"

Branch information:
  git branch /-r/-a
  git checkout <branchname>                  (Change the branch)

Remote repositories:
  git remote /-v
  git remote add <name> <url>